                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On November 17 the National Security Council submitted to President
                        <persName>Truman</persName>
                    <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 38/4 on the future courses of United States
                    action with respect to Austria. This paper <hi rend="italic">inter alia</hi>
                    analyzed the problem of Austrian internal security in terms of the formation of
                    an Austrian Army. The conclusions of the paper were then approved by President
                        <persName>Truman</persName> and its implementation was to be coordinated by
                    the Secretary of State. For the text of <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss>
                    38/4, see <ref target="#pg_1190">page 1190</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
